---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Jovie of Ann Arbor"
  description="Privacy policy for jovierecruiting.com. Learn how Jovie of Ann Arbor collects, uses, and protects your information."
>
  <Nav />
  <main>
    <section style="background-color: #FAFAF8; padding-top: clamp(7rem, 12vw, 11rem); padding-bottom: clamp(4rem, 7vw, 7rem);">
      <div class="container">
        <div style="max-width: 72ch;">
          <h1
            style="
              font-family: var(--font-display);
              font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
              font-weight: 700;
              letter-spacing: -0.03em;
              color: #1A2E38;
              margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
              line-height: 1.1;
            "
          >
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #4A6572; margin: 0 0 3rem 0;">Last updated: April 2026</p>

          <div style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #4A6572;">
            <p>This Privacy Policy describes how Jovie of Ann Arbor ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and shares information about you when you use jovierecruiting.com.</p>

            <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.375rem; color: #1A2E38; margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem 0;">Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>When you submit an application through our website, we collect your name, email address, phone number, and any other information you choose to provide. We may also collect standard analytics data such as pages visited and browser type.</p>

            <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.375rem; color: #1A2E38; margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem 0;">How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use the information you provide to contact you about employment opportunities at Jovie, schedule interviews, and communicate about your application status. If you opt in to SMS, we may send text messages related to your application.</p>

            <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.375rem; color: #1A2E38; margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem 0;">SMS Communications</h2>
            <p>By providing your phone number and checking the consent box on our application form, you agree to receive text messages from Jovie sent via an autodialer. Message frequency is approximately 4 messages per month. Message and data rates may apply. Text STOP to opt out at any time. Text HELP for more information. Your agreement to receive SMS is not a condition of any purchase.</p>

            <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.375rem; color: #1A2E38; margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem 0;">Sharing Your Information</h2>
            <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share your information with the Jovie national organization and with vetted families for placement purposes. We use third-party services including Web3Forms to process form submissions.</p>

            <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.375rem; color: #1A2E38; margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem 0;">Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:AnnArborMI@jovie.com" style="color: #1A475E;">AnnArborMI@jovie.com</a>. You can also review the Jovie national privacy policy at <a href="https://www.jovie.com/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #1A475E;">www.jovie.com/privacy-policy/</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
